Lokacin taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara taron neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia a daren yau.
Wannan ne na farko cikin tarurrukan Trump guda biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wuraren da masu jefa kuri'a ke son su, kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Tun da aka dakatar da zaben tabbatar da wanda ya zaɓa don kujerar da ta rage a Kotun Koli, Trump yana so ya ƙarfafa goyon baya ga zaɓen da ke tafe a tsakiyar lokacin mulkinsa, saboda Republicans na iya rasa iko a kan Majalisa bayan zaben da aka yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron zaben Trump a West Virginia a yau da dare, kuma a ina zan iya kallon shi a kan layi?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, an shirya shi ne a karfe 7:00 na yamma, Eastern Coast Time, a yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron zaben Trump a West Virginia ta yanar gizo ta hanyar bidiyo na YouTube a ƙasa.
Wataƙila Trump zai tattauna shari'ar da ake yi a wannan makon na Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi takarar kotun koli, wanda ya zama mai rikitarwa saboda zargin da ake yi game da lalata, yayin da ake dakatar da amincewar da ake tsammani a majalisar dattawa na tsawon mako guda don FBI ta bincika zargin.
Amma babban burin wannan taron na taron shine taimaka wa 'yan Republican, da ke fuskantar babban zaben a watan Nuwamba, su samu wasu wurare.
A cewarsa, masu yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump sun bayyana cewa manufar wannan taron na mako mai zuwa shine "samar da masu sa kai da magoya baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjayen da ke cikin majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai", in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafawa a kan majalisa yana da muhimmanci sosai ga shirinsa cewa shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da yawa kafin ya shiga cikin kakar yakin neman zabe mai cike da mutane", wani kakakin yakin Trump da ya ƙi a kira shi ya shaida wa Reuters.
An shirya taron a Wesbanco Arena da ke Wheeling, kuma ana iya ganin cewa taron zai jawo hankalin masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma za a yi ta ba da labari a cikin kafofin watsa labarai a Pittsburgh, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne za a yi wa Trump ziyara a Virginia ta Yamma a karo na biyu a cikin wata guda, jihar da ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin 100 a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na Jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ake gudanar da zabe.
"Gaskiyar cewa shugaban ya zo ne don ya yi kokarin tura shi cikin kuri'u ba kyakkyawan alama ba ce ga Morrisey", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
