Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder
Turai ta fara ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder da babbar fa'ida bayan ta kammala wasan hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar da ta yi 10-6 a gaban Amurka.
Ma'aurata masu ban sha'awa da suka hada da Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci harin da suka yi da nasara biyu a gaban Tiger Woods mai jinkiri, wanda ya kara yawan darajarsu a Le Golf National zuwa maki hudu.
Ƙungiyar Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, yayin da suke ƙoƙarin dawo da kyautar da suka yi a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, sun mamaye 'yan wasan Amurka da suka yi kuskure da yawa a gwajin hudu na safe kuma sun lashe gasar da kashi 3 zuwa 1.
Amurka ta yi tsayayya da juriya mai tsanani a gwajin foursome, inda ta lashe wasanni biyu amma ba ta iya rage rashi ba.
Jim Furyk ya bukaci maki takwas daga cikin wasannin da aka buga a ranar Lahadi don ya ci gaba da cin kofin.
Fleetwood shine farkon ɗan Turai na farko da ya sami maki huɗu a jere, kuma tare da Molinari, wani nau'i mai suna Molliwood bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki, su ne na biyu da suka sami maki huɗu daga cikin wasannin buɗewa huɗu a duk tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun ci Woods da Patrick Reed a gwajin 'yan wasan hudu, sun ci gaba da yin nasara sosai wajen doke Woods da kuma sabon dan wasan Amurka Bryson Dechambeau da ƙimar da ta fi kyau, 5-4.
Woods, wanda ya sha wahala a wasannin Asabar guda biyu, ya yi wasu glitches na gogewa, amma ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasanni 29 a huduballs da foursomes, daga cikinsu bakwai sun kasance a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ya huta a lokacin wasan hudu na safe, ya dawo tare da abokin aikinsa Henrik Stenson a gwajin huɗu kuma ya doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, matsayi na ɗaya da na uku a duniya.
Amma, ba a yi tafiya ba a wannan rana mai sanyi da kyau a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
