Johnny English ya sake buga: fim din 'yan leken asiri da Rowan Atkinson ya taka rawa
Ya zama al'ada a nemi ma'anar da ke tattare da Brexit a cikin kowane sabon fim na Burtaniya, amma wannan ba ya shafi sabon fim a cikin jerin jerin wasan kwaikwayo na fim din da ke dauke da Johnny English a matsayin babban mutum, jerin da suka fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma suka dawo rayuwa a 2011 tare da Johnny English ya dawo.
Shin wannan baƙar magana game da yadda muke da ban mamaki zai zama sabuwar damar fitarwa ga al'ummarmu?
Koyaya, Johnny English, ɗan leƙen asirin da ke da idanu masu ƙyalƙyali da fuskar roba, an sake sabunta lasisinsa na sau biyu don lalata komai. Sunan mutumin yana nufin, da farko, cewa shi ne babban abin dariya ga masu sauraron fina-finai a ƙasashen da ba sa jin Turanci.
Shi ne, ba shakka, mai ba da labari mai ban mamaki wanda, duk da ikirarinsa na alatu da kuma wadata, yana da ɗan Clouseau, wani ɗanɗano na Mr. Bean, da kuma ƙusa daga irin mutumin da ya ba da gudummawa ɗaya ga jigon kiɗa na Chariots of Fire a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta 2012 a London.
Wannan halin ya dogara ne akan mai bincike da kuma mutum marar gida mai ban mamaki wanda Atkinson ya yi a wani lokaci a cikin tallan TV na Barclaycard, wanda ya bar rikici a baya.
Wannan sabon abu na J.E. yana da lokaci mai kyau ko biyu.
Na ji daɗin ganin Johnny English ya zo kusa da wani jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu a cikin rigar ƙarni na farko, kuma ƙwanƙolin rotor ya yi saurin kai ga gashin kansa.
Kyautar Atkinson ga wasan kwaikwayo na jiki yana da kyau, amma yanayin jin dadi yana da rauni kuma, aƙalla, ba shi da amfani, musamman saboda fina-finai masu mahimmanci, kamar waɗanda suke cikin jerin 007 ko Mission Impossible, suna ba da tabbacin lokacin ban dariya a matsayin kayan aiki.
Kuma ban dariya ya fi dacewa da yara fiye da manya, kuma a ganina, abubuwan da Johnny English ya yi na ban dariya ba su da basira da basira kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi a fim dinsa na silent lokacin da yake wasa da Bean.
Kamar yadda aka saba, an ce Birtaniya tana da matsaloli masu tsanani.
Wani dan gwanin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin hanyar yanar gizo ta sirri ta Birtaniya ta hanyar gano ainihin 'yan sandan Ingila a ɓoye, don sa jami'in sabis ya yi sanyin gwiwa, wani aiki mai ban tausayi ga Kevin Eldon.
Wannan shi ne ƙarshen firaministan da ke da girma da kuma zama a ƙarƙashin ƙiyayya, wanda ya riga ya sha wahala daga mummunan rikici saboda raguwar shaharar siyasa: Emma Thompson tana yin duk abin da ta iya tare da mutuntakarta kamar Theresa May, amma rubutun ba ta ba ta damar yin haske.
Masu ba da rahoto na sirri sun sanar da ita cewa an yi wa dukkan 'yan leken asirin da ke aiki lahani, don haka dole ne ta kunna wani jami'in da ke cikin ajiya.
Wannan shi ne Johnny English kansa, wanda yanzu yake aiki a matsayin malamin makaranta a makarantar sakandare, amma kuma yana koyar da darasi game da yadda ake zama jami'in ɓoye. Ga wasu kyawawan gags, domin English yana gudanar da makarantar leken asiri kamar School of Rock.
An kawo English zuwa Whitehall don ganawar gaggawa, sai ya sake haduwa da abokin aikinsa na dā, Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake buga.
Bough yanzu ya auri wani kwamandan jirgin ruwa, wani mutum mai matukar farin ciki da daraja, rawar da baiwar Vicki Pepperdine ta ɗan ɓata.
Saboda haka, waɗannan Batman da Robin na ƙirƙirar rikice-rikice a cikin Sirrin Sirrin Mai Girma sun koma aiki, suna fuskantar kyakkyawan femme fatale Ophelia Bulletova, wanda Olga Kurylenko ta buga.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista ya shiga cikin sihiri na wani mai tallatawa mai tallatawa a masana'antar fasaha wanda ke da'awar zai iya magance matsalolin IT na Burtaniya: Jason Volta mai ban tsoro, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
English da Bough sun shiga wani labari mai ban tsoro: sun yi ado a matsayin masu hidima, sun ƙone gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai salo, sun haifar da rikici lokacin da suka shiga jirgin ruwa mai daraja na Volta, sannan English ya haifar da rashin jin daɗin tsari mai kyau lokacin da suka yi ƙoƙarin amfani da saitin tabarau na gaskiya don sanin abin da ke cikin gidan Volta.
Wannan fim din na karshe yana da matukar burgewa, amma duk da haka, duk da cewa fim din yana da kyau kuma mai launi, yana kama da shirin talabijin na yara.
Wani fim ne mai ban mamaki.
