Amurka na iya amfani da sojojin ruwa don toshe fitar da makamashi na Rasha, in ji Sakataren Cikin Gida
Washington na iya, idan ya cancanta, ta yi amfani da rundunar jiragen ruwa don hana makamashin Rasha isa wasu kasuwannin, har da gabas ta tsakiya, in ji Sakataren harkokin cikin gida na Amurka, Ryan Zinke, wanda Washington Examiner ta ruwaito.
Zinke ya ce, yadda Rasha ta yi amfani da makamashi a Syria, musamman a inda take aiki a kan gayyatar gwamnati mai kyau, dalili ne na bincika sababbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Ina ganin dalilin da ya sa nake cikin gabas ta tsakiya shi ne domin ina son in yi amfani da wutar lantarki wajen sayar da wutar lantarki kamar yadda nake yi a gabashin Turai da kuma kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
