Ramirez ta yi ikirarin cewa wanda aka nada a kotun koli ya nuna mata gabobin jikinsu a lokacin da suke halartar wani biki yayin da suke dalibai a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Mai kirkiro yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin kafa sabuwar intanet don yin gasa da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ta duniya, ya kaddamar da wani kamfani wanda yake son yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin da ya yi wa wannan babban mashahurin mai fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne da ke amfani da dandalin Open Source na Berners-Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma wanda ke da damar samun damar yin amfani da bayanan.
A wata hira da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi dariya cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Yanzu dole ne mu yi haka", ya ce game da farawa.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don ba mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu archives na bayanan sirri na kan layi ko PODs.
Yana iya ɗauke da jerin sunayen tuntuɓar, shirye-shirye, kalandar, ɗakunan karatu na kiɗa ko wasu kayan aiki na mutum da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify suna samuwa a cikin burauzar guda ɗaya, duk a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke da ban mamaki game da wannan adana bayanan sirri na kan layi shi ne cewa mai amfani yana da cikakken iko akan wanda zai iya samun damar wannan nau'in bayanin.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "karfafawa ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar Shugaba John Bruce, manufar Inrupt ita ce ta ba da albarkatu, matakai da kuma ƙwarewa masu dacewa don yin amfani da Solid ga kowa.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, ƙungiyar masu haɓaka da ke aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen shirye-shiryen aikin sa kai.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu bunkasa fasaha a duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen kansu na waje ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da Facebook da Google game da ko za su yi cikakken canji ko a'a lokacin da tsarin kasuwancin su ya zama gaba daya ba tare da ɓata lokaci ba.
Ba mu nemi izinin su ba.
A wani rubutu da ya wallafa a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "Mishin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu wanda zai taimaka wajen kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon intanet a Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya sauya Intanet ta wajen kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin da suka gabata, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na Intanet.
Ko da bayan da ya kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance wanda ya kafa kuma ya jagoranci World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation, da Open Data Institute.
"Ina da tabbaci sosai game da wannan zamani na Intanet", in ji Berners-Lee.
