Ronaldo ya musanta zargin fyade yayin da lauyoyi ke shirin kai karar mujallar Jamus
Cristiano Ronaldo ya ce zargin da ake masa shi ne fake news kuma wasu mutane suna son yin tallace-tallace da sunansa.
Lauyoyinsa sun yanke shawarar kai karar mujallar Jamus ta Der Spiegel, wadda ta wallafa zargin.
An zargi dan wasan Portugal da Juventus da yin fyade da wata mata 'yar Amurka, mai suna Kathryn Mayorga, a wani otal a Las Vegas a shekarar 2009.
Jaridar Der Spiegel ta ruwaito a ranar Juma'a cewa dan wasan ya biya ta dala 375,000 don kada ta yi magana game da lamarin.
Bayan 'yan sa'o'i bayan da aka gabatar da tuhumar, a cikin wani bidiyo da aka watsa a Instagram Live na mabiyansa miliyan 142, Ronaldo mai shekaru 33 ya ce wannan labari ne na karya.
"Babu, ba, ba, ba, ba.
Abin da suka ce a yau fake news ne, "in ji mai lashe kyautar Ballon d'Or a gaban kyamarar bidiyo.
Suna son yin tallace-tallace da sunana.
Hakan na al'ada ne.
Suna son su zama sanannu ta wurin kiran sunana, amma na saba da hakan.
"Ni mutum ne mai farin ciki kuma duk abin da ke cikinta yana da kyau", in ji mai kunnawa, yana murmushi.
Lauyoyin Ronaldo na shirin kai karar Der Spiegel kan wadannan zarge-zargen, wanda suka kira "Reacceptable Reporting of Suspicions of Privacy", a cewar Reuters.
Lauyan kungiyar ta Christian Schertz ya ce, 'yan wasan za su nemi fansa don lalata dabi'unsu da kuma yadda suka aikata laifin da ya fi tsanani a 'yan shekarun nan.
An yi zargin cewa an yi wannan hatsarin ne a watan Yuni na shekara ta 2009, a wani Apartment da ke cikin Palms Hotel and Casino a Las Vegas.
Bayan sun hadu a wata kulob, Ronaldo da Mayorga sun koma ɗakin dan wasan, inda ya yi mata fyade, a cewar takardun da aka shigar a Kotun Yankin Clark County, Nevada.
Mayorga ta ce bayan lamarin, Ronaldo ya durƙusa a gabanta kuma ya gaya mata cewa shi yaro ne mai kyau a kashi 99 cikin 100 na mutane, kuma an ci amanarsa ta hanyar kashi 1.
Takardar ta ce Ronaldo ya tabbatar da cewa ya yi jima'i da mai tuhumar, amma hakan na nufin cewa ya yi jima'i da ita.
Mayorga ta yi ikirarin cewa ta je ga 'yan sanda kuma an yi hotunan raunukanta a asibiti, amma daga bisani ta amince da yarjejeniya a waje da kotun saboda an hana ta yiwuwar ramawa kuma ta damu da cewa za a wulakanta ta a fili.
Matar mai shekara 34 yanzu tana neman soke yarjejeniyar domin har yanzu tana cikin damuwa da abin da ya faru.
A lokacin da aka zarge shi da kai hari, Ronaldo yana shirin komawa Real Madrid daga Manchester United. A wannan bazarar, an canja shi zuwa Juventus, babbar kungiyar Italiya, bayan da ya samu yuro miliyan 100.
Brexit: Birtaniya za ta yi nadamar rasa masana'antun mota har abada
Birtaniya za ta yi nadama har abada idan ta rasa matsayin ta na jagora a duniya a cikin samar da motoci bayan Brexit, in ji Sakataren harkokin kasuwanci Greg Clark.
Ya kara da cewa yana da matukar damuwa cewa Toyota UK ta fada wa BBC cewa idan Birtaniya ta fita daga EU ba tare da wata yarjejeniya ba, za ta dakatar da samar da ita a masana'antar ta a Burnaston, kusa da Derby.
"Muna bukatar yarjejeniya", in ji Clark.
