Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ce za a sake jinkirta taron Trump da Rosenstein
Babban taron Donald Trump da Mataimakin Babban Shari'a Rod Rosenstein na iya dagewa har mako guda, saboda gwagwarmayar neman Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada a kotun koli, ya ci gaba, fadar White House ta ce a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein yana lura da mai ba da shawara na musamman Robert Mueller, wanda ke bincika tsoma baki na Rasha a cikin zaɓen, alaƙar da ke tsakanin taimakon Trump da Rasha, da yiwuwar hana shari'a ta shugaban.
Labarai game da yiwuwar Trump ya sallami mataimakin babban lauya, yana barazana ga 'yancin kai na Mueller, sun kasance suna yawo a cikin Washington na watanni.
A farkon watan, The New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya tattauna game da yiwuwar saka makirufo don yin rikodin tattaunawar da Trump da kuma yiwuwar dakatar da shugaban ta hanyar Kwaskwarima na 25 na Tsarin Mulki na Amurka.
Rosenstein ya musanta wannan rahoton.
Amma a watan Litinin da ya gabata ya tafi fadar White House, kuma rahotanni sun ce yana shirin barin aiki.
A maimakon haka, an sanar da cewa za su gana da Trump a ranar Alhamis, wanda a lokacin yana zaune a hedkwatar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a New York.
Trump ya ce ya fi son kada ya sallami Rosenstein, amma sai aka jinkirta taron don kauce wa rikici da sauraron majalisar dokokin Amurka, inda Kavanaugh da ɗaya daga cikin matan da suka zarge shi da cin zarafin jima'i, Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, suka ba da shaida.
A ranar Juma'a, Trump ya bukaci FBI ta gudanar da bincike na tsawon mako guda kan zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh, wanda ya sake jinkirta zaben majalisar dattawa.
Sakataren yada labarai na Trump, Sarah Sanders, ta bayyana a gidan talabijin na Fox News a ranar Lahadi.
A lokacin da aka tambaye ta game da ganawar da ta yi da Rosenstein, ta ce: "Ba a riga an kafa kwanan wata ba don haka. Zai iya zama wannan makon ko kuma za a iya jinkirta shi da mako guda, la'akari da duk sauran abubuwan da ke faruwa a yanzu a Kotun Koli.
Amma za mu ga kuma ina son in ci gaba da kula da jaridu.
Wasu 'yan jarida sun yi ikirarin cewa Sanders bai yi jawabi ba a fadar White House tun ranar 10 ga watan Satumba.
Mai gidan Chris Wallace ya tambaye ni dalilin.
Sanders ya ce rage yawan gabatarwa ba saboda rashin son jaridar TV ba ne, ko da yake ya kara da cewa: "Ba na musun cewa suna son yin gabatarwa".
Sai ya ce za a kara samun lamba tsakanin Trump da manema labarai.
Shugaban kasa yana halartar taro da yawa fiye da duk shugabannin da suka gabata, in ji ta, ba tare da ambaton wata hujja ba: Mun bincika lambobin.
Sanders ya ce za a ci gaba da gudanar da taron, amma na fi so a ba manema labarai damar yin tambayoyi kai tsaye ga shugaban Amurka, ba ni ba.
Muna kokarin yin hakan a mafi yawan lokuta kuma kun ga mun yi hakan a lokuta da dama a cikin makonni da suka gabata, kuma tattaunawa da shugaban Amurka zai maye gurbin gabatar da labarai a lokacin da yake samuwa.
A kullum, Trump yana amsa tambayoyi a lokacin da ya bar fadar White House ko kuma yana halartar tarurruka na bude ido ko kuma taron manema labarai da manyan jami'an da suka ziyarce shi.
Ba a yawan yin taron manema labarai da shi kaɗai ba.
A wannan makon a birnin New York, shugaban ya nuna dalilin da ya sa hakan yake faruwa ta hanyar yin wani abu mai ban mamaki da ya faru a gaban 'yan jarida.
Wani Sakataren Harkokin Kiwon Lafiya ya rubuta wa ma'aikatan Hukumar Kiwon Lafiya ta Kasa (NHS) a Scotland game da tsoron Brexit
Sakataren ya rubuta wa ma'aikatan EU da ke aiki a NHS Scotland don nuna godiyarsa a madadin kasar da kuma son su zauna bayan Brexit.
Jeane Freeman, 'yar majalisa a Scotland, ta aika da wasikar a cikin yanayi na kasa da watanni shida kafin Birtaniya ta fice daga Tarayyar Turai.
Gwamnatin Scotland ta riga ta ɗauki alhakin ɗaukar nauyin biyan kuɗin neman zama na dindindin ga 'yan ƙasar EU da ke aiki a cikin ayyukan gwamnati na rarraba.
A cikin wasiƙarsa, Freeman ya rubuta: "A lokacin rani, tattaunawar janyewar tsakanin Birtaniya da EU ta ci gaba, ana sa ran yanke shawara a wannan kaka.
Amma gwamnatin Burtaniya ta fara shirya kanta sosai don wani yanayi daban, inda babu yarjejeniya don fita daga EU.
Na san cewa lokaci ne mai matukar damuwa a gare ku.
Saboda haka, ina son in sake nuna yadda nake godiya ga gudummawar kowane ma'aikaci, ko da wane irin ƙasa ne.
A cikin ƙungiyarmu da kuma wajenmu, abokan aikinmu suna da ƙwarewa da ƙwarewa masu kyau waɗanda ke ƙarfafa da kuma inganta aikin kiwon lafiya, kuma suna amfanar marasa lafiya da al'ummomin da muke bauta wa.
Za ka iya yin tunanin Scotland gida kuma muna son ka zauna a nan.
Christion Abercrombie ya yi aikin tiyata na gaggawa bayan ya ji rauni a kai
Dan wasan Tennessee State Tigers, Christion Abercrombie, ya yi aikin tiyata na gaggawa bayan ya ji rauni a kan kansa a ranar Asabar, a wasan da tawagarsa ta yi wa Vanderbilt Commodores wasa, 31-27, in ji Mike Organ na Tennessee.
Kocin Tennessee State Rod Reed ya gaya wa manema labarai cewa an yi harin ne jim kaɗan kafin hutu.
"Ya kai ga layin cusa kuma ya fadi", in ji Reed.
