Ga wasu girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa ta afku a gabar yamma ta lardin Aceh na Indonesia, a arewacin tsibirin Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami wanda ya shafi kasashe 14, ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar mutane 226,000 a gabar Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su na Aceh.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa yammacin tsibirin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 6.8 a sikelin Richter ta afkawa kudu da tsibirin Java, tsibirin Indonesia mafi yawan jama'a, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa gabar kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.6 a sikelin Richter ya faru kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
