An kama dan Sarah Palin a kan zargin da ake masa na yin lalata da maza da mata
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa, Sarah Palin, an kama shi bisa zargin tashin hankali.
An kama Palin, mai shekaru 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin yin ta'addanci a gida, yana da hannu a cikin shigar da kara game da ta'addanci a gida da kuma adawa da kama shi, a cewar wani rahoto da 'yan sanda na jihar Alaska suka wallafa a ranar Asabar.
Rahoton ya ce, sa'ad da wani da ya san shi da mata ya kira 'yan sanda don su yi zargin laifin da suka aikata, sai suka karɓe wayarsa.
An tsare Palin ne a gidan 'yan sanda a Mat-Su, inda ake jiran a yi masa shari'a, kuma an tsare shi ne a kan wani asusu na ba da belin da ya kai dala 500, in ji KTUU.
Ya bayyana a gaban kotu a ranar Asabar, inda ya bayyana cewa ba shi da laifi a lokacin da aka nemi ya yi ikirarinsa, a cewar cibiyar sadarwa.
Palin yana fuskantar tuhuma uku na aikata laifuka na aji A, wanda ke nufin zai iya yin kurkuku har zuwa shekara guda kuma a yi masa tarar dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da aikata laifi na aji B, wanda ke da hukuncin ɗaurin kurkuku na kwana ɗaya da kuma tarar dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shi ne karo na farko da ake zargin Palin da hakan ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an zarge shi da zalunci a kan mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don sanar da zargin da ake yi mata.
Ana sauraron wannan shari'ar a kotun tsofaffin sojoji ta Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an zarge shi da aikata zalunci a gida, yana da hannu a cikin wani da'awar aikata zalunci a gida, kuma yana da makami yayin da yake cikin maye dangane da wani abin da ya faru.
A cewar wata sanarwa da budurwarsa ta yi, ya yi mata dūka a fuska.
Sarah Palin ta fuskanci sukar daga kungiyoyin tsofaffi a shekarar 2016 bayan an danganta halin da ɗanta ya yi da ciwon zuciya na post-traumatic stress disorder da yake fama da shi bayan ya kasance cikin sojojin Iraqi.
Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia: Daruruwan mutane sun mutu
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu bayan girgizar kasa ta afku a tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 a sikelin Richter ta jawo tsunami kuma ta lalata dubban gidaje.
An lalata wutar lantarki da kuma hanyoyin sadarwa, kuma ana sa ran mutuwar za ta ƙaru a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar ta afku a yankin Sulawesi da ke arewa maso gabashin Jakarta, babban birnin kasar.
A shafukan sada zumunta, ana samun bidiyo na lokacin da aka yi hakan.
Dubban mutane suna wurin wani biki a bakin teku a birnin Palu lokacin da tsunami ya afku a bakin tekun.
Kotun tarayya na neman hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York
Kotun tarayya ta New York ta bukaci hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas, wanda ba a taɓa yin hukuncin kisa a jihar ba saboda aikata laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
Sai dai Saipov mai shekara 30 ya yi amfani da wata babbar motar hayar Home Depot don kai hari a kan wata hanyar keke a West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya kai wa masu tafiya da kuma masu hawa keke hari a kan hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don a yi musu hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara suna bukatar su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe wadanda suka mutu takwas da gangan kuma ya yi musu mummunan rauni, a cewar sanarwar da aka bayar game da bukatar kisa da aka shigar a kotun ta Kudu ta New York.
Dukkanin masu tuhuma za su iya samun hukuncin kisa, a cewar takardar kotu.
Bayan 'yan makonni daga harin, babban kotun tarayya ta zargi Saipov da manyan zargi 22 wanda ya haɗa da zargin kisa takwas na goyon bayan aikata laifuka, wanda masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da su a cikin shari'o'in aikata laifuka, da kuma zargi na tashin hankali da lalata motocin.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci babban shiri da gangan, inda suka bayyana yadda Saipov ya aikata laifin da ake kira "m, mummunan da kuma lalata".
Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa iyalan da abokansa rauni, wahala da asarar rayuka: Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, a cewar sanarwar niyya.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe masu yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekara goma ta shige tun da aka yi shari'ar kisa a kotun New York.
An zargi ɗan'uwansa, Khalid Barnes, da kisan 'yan kasuwa biyu, amma a ƙarshe an yanke masa hukuncin rai a watan Satumba na 2009.
An yanke hukuncin kisa na karshe a cikin wani shari'ar tarayya a New York a 1953 ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata biyu da aka kashe bayan da aka yanke musu hukuncin kisa bisa zargin yin ta'addanci ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War, shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe ma'aurata Rosenberg a kan kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cewar takardun kotu, Saipov, dan kasar Uzbekistan, bai nuna nadamarsa ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
Ya shaida wa masu binciken cewa yana farin ciki da abin da ya yi, in ji 'yan sanda.
Saipov ya shaidawa hukumomi cewa ya ji ya samu wahayi zuwa kai harin bayan ya kalli bidiyon kungiyar ISIS a wayarsa, a cewar mai karbar karar.
Ya kuma bukaci a saka tutar ISIS a cikin dakin asibiti.
Ya yi ikirarin cewa bai yi laifi ba a kan zargin da ake masa na 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu kare hakkin Saipov a ofishin, ya ce ya yi matukar takaici da hukuncin da kotun ta yanke.
"Mun yi imanin cewa hukuncin kisa, maimakon a yi masa da'awar da ya yi da'awar cewa ya yi laifi da zai kai ga rai ba tare da yiwuwar sake shi ba, zai ƙara wa dukan mutanen da suka yi wannan laifi da ke cikin wannan lamarin raɗaɗin raɗaɗin rai", in ji Patton.
A baya, ƙungiyar masu kare Saipov ta nemi kotu ta hana ta yin amfani da hukuncin kisa.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Conservative ya ce dole ne NIGEL FARAGE ya jagoranci tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin a yau cewa zai karfafa sojojin farar hula a lokacin zanga-zangar da aka yi a taron jam'iyyar Conservative.
Tsohon shugaban Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa su ji matsa lamba daga masu son ganin kudin Tarayyar Turai, bayan wata 'yar majalisa Theresa May ta ce ya kamata ta kasance a gaba wajen tattaunawa da Tarayyar Turai.
Peter Bone, dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Conservative, ya bayyana a wani zanga-zanga a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya za ta fita a yanzu idan Farage ya kasance Sakatare a yakin Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da May ke fuskanta game da sansanonin da suka rabu sosai ya kara da cewa 'yan jam'iyyar Conservative sun shiga wani zanga-zanga na neman ficewar kungiyar daga Tarayyar Turai da aka shirya a birnin.
Firayim Ministan yana aiki tuƙuru don sa shirinsa na sasantawa, wanda ake kira shirin Chequers, ya gudana yadda ya kamata, yana fuskantar hare-hare daga masu goyon bayan barin Tarayyar Turai, waɗanda suke son su kasance a ciki, da kuma daga Tarayyar Turai.
Allies sun nuna cewa za ta ci gaba da ƙoƙarin cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels, ko da menene sakamakon, kuma za ta tilasta masu tsinkaye da kuma Labour su zabi tsakanin tayin da haos.
Bone ya ce a taron da ake kira 'Leave Means Leave' a Solihull cewa yana son a daina shirin Chequers.
Ya ba da shawarar cewa Farage ya kasance cikin tawagar kuma ya ba da alhakin tattaunawar da ke tattare da Brussels.
"Idan ya yi wa'azi, ba za mu kasance a cikin Tarayyar Turai ba", in ji shi.
'Yan majalisa masu tsaron gida, wato 'yan majalisa na Wellingborough, sun ce: 'Ina goyon bayan Brexit, amma dole ne mu yi watsi da shirin Chequers.
Da yake magana game da hamayyarsa ga Tarayyar Turai, ya ce: "Ba mu yi yaƙi a yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya don mu zama bayi ba.
Muna son mu yi dokokinmu a ƙasarmu.
Bone ya musanta shawarwarin sauya ra'ayin jama'a a zaben 2016: "Ba gaskiya ba ne cewa Birtaniya ta canza tunani kuma suna son su kasance a cikin EU.
Andrea Jenkyns, memba na jam'iyyar Conservative Party da ke goyon bayan Brexit, ta kuma halarci zanga-zangar kuma ta gaya wa manema labarai: "Ina so in ce kawai: Madam Firayim Minista, ku saurari muryoyin mutane.
'Yan siyasa ba sa goyon bayan shirin Chequers, 'yan adawa ba sa goyon bayan shi, jam'iyyarmu ba ta goyon bayan shi ba, kuma 'yan adawarmu da ke fitowa a kan titi suna goyon bayanmu a zaben.
Ka daina shirin Chequers ka fara saurara.
A cikin wata sako da ta aika wa Theresa May, ta kara da cewa: "Prime ministers da ke riƙe da aikinsu su ne wadanda ke cika alkawuran su.
A lokacin taron, Nigel Farage ya ce dole ne a sa 'yan siyasa su ji matsa lamba idan suna shirin yin watsi da shawarar da aka yanke a zaben 2016.
Ya ce, "Wannan batun amincewa ne tsakanin mu mutane da kuma 'yan siyasa.
Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit kuma muna nan a yau don gaya musu cewa ba za mu bar su su yi hakan ba.
A cikin sakon da ya aika wa masu farin ciki, ya kara da cewa: "Ina son ku taimaka mana mu matsa lamba a kan 'yan siyasarmu, wadanda ke shirin cin amanar Brexit.
Muna karfafa sojojin kasar da suka kawo mana nasara a Brexit kuma ba za mu daina ba har sai mun zama Burtaniya mai zaman kanta, mai zaman kanta da alfahari.
A halin yanzu, masu goyon bayan kasancewa a cikin Tarayyar Turai sun yi ta yawo a Birmingham kafin taron sa'o'i biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
Wasu 'yan adawa sun ɗaga wasu banners da ke cewa ' 'Masu Tsananin Ƙasa suna adawa da Brexit' bayan an kaddamar da kungiyar a karshen mako.
Lord Adonis, wani dan jam'iyyar Labour, ya yi dariya game da 'yan jam'iyyar Conservative da kuma matsalolin tsaro da suka fuskanta a lokacin da suka fara taron.
"Waɗannan mutane ne suke gaya mana cewa za su iya tura tsarin IT da duk fasahar da za a iya amfani da su a Kanada, don yin amfani da fasahar dijital, don yin kasuwanci ba tare da takunkumi ba a Ireland", ya kara da cewa.
Wannan baƙar magana ce.
Ya kara da cewa, Brexit ba zai kawo amfanin ba.
Warren yana shirin yin tunani sosai game da takarar shugaban kasa
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Amurka ta ce za ta yi tunani sosai game da takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben watan Nuwamba.
A cewar jaridar Boston Globe, Sanata 'yar Democrat ta Massachusetts ta yi magana game da makomar ta a ranar Asabar a wani taron majalisar dattawa a yammacin jihar Massachusetts.
Warren, mai yawan sukar shugaban kasa Donald Trump, tana neman neman takararsa a zaben Nuwamba a kan Geoff Diehl, dan majalisar wakilai na jam'iyyar Republican, wanda ya kasance shugaban yakin neman zaben Donald Trump na 2016 a Massachusetts.
Ta kasance a tsakiyar tsinkaye cewa za ta iya doke Trump a shekarar 2020.
A ranar Asabar da yamma a garin Holyoke, taron na 36 da aka yi da 'yan ƙasa masu jefa kuri'a a cikin tsarin majalisa tun lokacin da Trump ya zama shugaban kasa.
Wani mai halartar taron ya tambaye ta ko tana son takarar shugaban kasa.
Warren ya amsa cewa lokaci ya yi da mata za su isa Washington don magance matsalolin gwamnatinmu da ke fama da mummunan rauni kuma wannan ya haɗa da mace a gabansa.
An kama wani wanda ake zargi da mutuwar da ta yi sanadiyar mutuwar dan wasan Sims a tawagar LSU
'Yan sanda a Baton Rouge, Los Angeles, sun sanar a ranar Asabar cewa an kama wani wanda ake zargi da mutuwar da ta yi sanadiyar mutuwar dan wasan kwando na LSU, Wayde Sims a ranar Juma'a.
