Labarai game da ruwan damina: Ƙarƙashin taro a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahoton da Hukumar kare dabbobi ta Florida ta fitar a yanzu ya nuna cewa yawan ruwan sama na ruwan sama a yankin Tampa Bay ya ragu.
A cewar Hukumar, an samu rashin daidaituwa a wuraren da ke Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier, wanda ke nuna cewa an rage yawan kwayoyin halitta.
Wannan ruwan sama na ruwan sama yana da nisa a fadin gabar teku na kimanin kilomita 210, daga arewacin Pinellas County zuwa kudu da Lee County.
Ana iya samun wuraren da ke da nisan mil 10 daga garin Hillsborough, amma a wurare da yawa fiye da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da ruwan sama a gundumar Pasco.
An ruwaito matsakaitan da ke cikin Pinellas County ko kuma a wajensa a makon da ya gabata, da kuma ƙananan da kuma manyan da ke cikin Hillsborough County, da ƙananan da ke cikin Manatee County, da ƙananan da ke cikin Sarasota County ko kuma a wajensa, da ƙananan da ke cikin Charlotte County, da ƙananan da ke cikin Lee County da wajensa, da ƙananan da ke cikin Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahoton rashin lafiyar numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da Collier Counties.
Babu wani rahoton cutar ta numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
